Priscilla Okyere (amụrụ na 6 June 1995) bụ onye Ghana na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agbachitere etiti etiti maka otu Lithuanian Gintra Universitetas na otu ụmụ nwanyị nke Ghana
Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Fabulous Ladies F.C
tupu ọ banye Fabulous L ladies F.C..
Okyere sonyere Ghana na 2018 Africa Women Cup of Nations, na-egwu egwuregwu abụọ.
